75
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:22,880
I'm sorry.

76
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:25,960
I'm sorry.

77
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,490
Dailing,

78
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,680
