89
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,400
I'm sorry.

90
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,120
I'm sorry.

91
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
Dailing,

92
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:31,240
