104
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:13,800
Ang Wei.

105
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,160
Ang Wei.

106
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,400
Dai Ling.

107
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:36,159
Ruan Nila.

108
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,840
Ruan Nila.

109
